item.description:
Another great outing to get some good folks together for a nice round of golf. This one will be on Saturday, July 24th at the Newton Commonwealth Golf course. Here's the link to see the layout of the course. http://www.sterlinggo...

I'm not sure of the tee time right now, but can book up to 5 days in advance. So I will call on Tuesday, July 20th for a tee time. Late morning will most likely be requested.

Attendees are responsible for their own green fees, and required to bring $1 on golf day for website maintenance.

Let me know if you have any questions. Look forward to seeing who can make it!

Thanks
Chuck Robbins
cerobbins2@yahoo.com
Cell phone (303) 246-3105
